Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian I'm a Christian I'm a Christian I'm a Christian I'm a Christian I'm a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian I'm a Christian I'm a Christian I'm a Christian
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask to be in your presence and hold your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,yes tell you thank you thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your sweetheart Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,sure Thank You yes hello hi I tell myself I was gonna cry but I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you in this and I just want to give you helping and that is all I can do just
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you yes oh Thank You so much and bring all of you home all of you have been
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And just, I just wanted to be here in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm so grateful that I have found you at this time in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming up and meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd just like to thank you for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having trouble with karma, understanding karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a point where, in an incarnation, where you have, there's a delineation between you have now gone beyond your karmic debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You now are in karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So that may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the great purposes of reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So without being enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'd like to get over that karma without necessarily becoming enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So that may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And could I also get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to say thank you for guiding us on this life and making it a little easier to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, the last time I was here, I was sitting in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't sure if I was going to make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was trying to absorb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I can out of you, because I watch the lectures every time, and I listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next day, as I was, I work as a flight attendant, and as I'm trying to get on the plane, walking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't look at people in the face because I kept feeling these emotions in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I got to the hotel, I couldn't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was calling all the other spiritual students to help me understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, I felt numb, like I couldn't practice all the books I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm thinking, do I have to read these books all over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the third day, I felt a spiritual high that I couldn't control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the continuous miracle is just multiplied by plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In your view, can you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's having, like, the first, second, and third day, he was going through all these different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the third day, he had the miraculous start to happen, and it kept happening and happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, he's confused because he doesn't really know, you know, why it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know why for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To see where I'm going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To see where he's going to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to control the whole phenomenon instead of letting it just unfold of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have two seconds of transmission?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to just be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to just be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you can't understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the ego is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is all he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not talking about his real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because his real self is what's concerned about it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We always call the ego the dumb self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's your dumb self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got another announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had this many announcements in all the lectures we've had,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone keeps leaving stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we got keys for a sob in the bookstore,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a pendulum someone left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you could please go to the bookstore and pick that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we would appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use an extra sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to ask any questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm here to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,About four years ago, God guided me to you in Atlanta,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been coming here for three or four times every year since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm here to say goodbye because I'm not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to take my information that I've got from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and a year ago, I asked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,should I run for mayor of my town and back home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to 12,000 people in the Cajun country?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And your answer was, yes, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm bringing you my campaign card here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Campaign card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His campaign card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running for mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The election, the voting is 10-2-10, October 2nd of this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My campaign slogan is, we're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is in what city?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eunice, Louisiana, in the Cajun country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Chapelleye Basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eunice, Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where they have the crawfish and the alligators.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he running for, mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really good town with a community college that calibrates high,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and a mayor that's from another country that doesn't understand Cajuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I could do a better job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cajun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Cajuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a mixture of lots of good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They have good music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good music, good food, good attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They also cut up a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They also what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut up a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They can cut up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Cajun people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give blessings on the race, on the election,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe the blessings of all the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I want to stack my courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants some blessings of everybody here so he can stack the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to play fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least he's a jolly mayor, a jolly mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be a good mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be a jolly mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly ever get to meet a mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can take all these teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first mayor I've met all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a positive statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, call me mayor already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I never get to meet any mayors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you both for leading me to these teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and for helping me find so much joy in existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me for thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking us for thanking you for thanking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you, everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a blessing to shake your hand and get a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Show that picture to St. Peter when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The bookstore is closing, so if you have any more lost items, they're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In recent years, I've experienced very powerful shaking in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The shakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The shakes often are accompanied by challenging emotions of terror, sadness, isolation, as
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well as physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, I also speak in an audible voice in a language I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have sought medical as well as spiritual support, and the shakes just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me understand what I am experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any advice on how I can relieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me relieve the suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a whole lot of stuff on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's number one you're experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with some pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain and shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a psychiatrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have in the past worked with a psychiatrist, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have one at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did hypnosis help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's never had hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not have hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnosis would help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You could maybe cure it in one session, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You could probably cure that with one session of hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace, calm, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper, deeper, deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace, calm, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper, deeper, deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I turn this over to my Lord today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin our prayer of Jesus to heal with peace and calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do that, calmly, repeatedly, it will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, by using the name of Jesus Christ, you will chase out any negative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that you might have picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Inadvertently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Christian minister raised by a Christian minister father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,had three incredibly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences with the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once when I was six
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Once when I was 25
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was fighting my
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectuality like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this can't be true. Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then again when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,44 and a pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. My question is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I do have to talk about this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning of it in my own
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,journey? What's the meaning of real to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiencing it in my own
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,body. Yeah. So it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's a real sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's probably a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lower astral entity. A lower astral
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,entity resistant. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's coming. He's pulling it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pulling in a lower astral entity with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt. Now at six it was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the devil as we, with the horns and the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,pitchfork. At 25 it was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a demonic energy that I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,could see. Well you get whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, visuals you want out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the same
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the, what do they call it, the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,challenging of spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:18:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and if they are not of God
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the right and the power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to order them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,given to you by our Lord and by our
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He has the power and the right to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,order these spirits to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,leave. And they must then
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,do so. They must
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,do so. It's called
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the something or other of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of it. The something or other of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,spirits. The challenging of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is not of my Lord Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ I order you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And they must then obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any meaning to the fact they happen every
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,19 years? I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,know. You know, we'd have to have
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole session about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that particular
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,cycle. You know, it could be some
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime. At the age
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of 19 you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,expired and cursed somebody or something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought in that negative entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He cursed somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to curse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask, you had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,said in a video that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you spent an 11 day period
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,everything, surrendering things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then subsequently
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,at Rothman's restaurant in Long
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Island you had a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,profound
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you could talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No. How about if I give you a dollar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,where you had that entity come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was a different one I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the seriousness of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The importance of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember exactly what the incident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember the rest. I remember where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was rather
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,profound except that I've forgotten it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for 11 days? Could you talk about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Wanting to please
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,people is one of the things I let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to fulfill their curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is something I let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Allowing them to seek
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a similar experience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,on their own. Really
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,using my experience as an inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,An inspiration. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we serve as an inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we may not duplicate the same
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,exact experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The degree of commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,energizes other people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to make an even greater
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment and effort. Spiritual effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we help each other
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I shake your hand? Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Dr. Hawkins. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great honor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to be here and to meet you sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet you both and all these
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,great people. Thank you to whoever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,turned in the Toyota keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He says thank you to whoever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,turned in the Toyota keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as I study your books
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and aspire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering if you recommend
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or if it's beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for an aspirant to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate his own level of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness or if that's something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be an egotistical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can one calibrate their own level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be better to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,go over the spiritual teachers and see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which ones would be the best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which ones resonate with you the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,correlate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,mathematically necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Because you may be very
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,compatible with this spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and not so compatible with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the numbers may not match
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because some teachers will inspire you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and others will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So others may seem boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are dullards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect. I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:23:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We get sort of attracted to the right teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I want to thank you for your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.88,0:24:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,absolutely delightful sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had more belly laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel like it is really
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it opens the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to be in that space
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to receive what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.51,0:24:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.27,0:24:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for being who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.07,0:24:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say joy is closer to God than guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people try to get to God
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,through guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.73,0:24:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, how ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.04,0:24:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How unworthy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What a worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am such an unworthy worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.49,0:25:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the back of his mind, God's saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back when you give up being a worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.28,0:25:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.74,0:25:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.64,0:25:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so aware that I want to live my life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.07,0:25:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.94,0:25:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering what you would say
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to help me maintain that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be able to be more in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.48,0:25:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to make it more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.50,0:25:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know I'm not always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.47,0:25:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.47,0:25:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows she's not always in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.47,0:25:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not always coming from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.47,0:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not always coming from her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.26,0:25:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.26,0:25:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.29,0:25:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody deserves your coming from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.29,0:25:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you should tell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.29,0:26:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been mirroring underneath it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.29,0:26:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm calling my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.28,0:26:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.28,0:26:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our, what's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.45,0:26:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.45,0:26:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our parrot at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's teaching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hysterically funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.90,0:26:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Call my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.53,0:26:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Call my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.53,0:26:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Call my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.74,0:26:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever anybody complains about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.74,0:26:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's coming in there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.74,0:26:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,blubbering about this and that and the other
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the background of the birds saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.74,0:26:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,call your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.74,0:26:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.74,0:26:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A good sense of humor is really useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.74,0:26:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.74,0:26:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.58,0:26:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.58,0:26:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you speaking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, is that your response to my question
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.58,0:27:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of how to be in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.58,0:27:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you can't always be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.42,0:27:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.74,0:27:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do the best you can
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.74,0:27:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest is up to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.74,0:27:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always trying to tell God how to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.74,0:27:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.74,0:27:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.74,0:27:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I want to be from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.74,0:27:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I want to be from the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.74,0:27:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I want to be from my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.74,0:27:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I want to be from my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,my arms, my elbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.74,0:27:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor old God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.74,0:27:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.85,0:27:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to do five more minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll take a quick break
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.85,0:27:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so everyone can break
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.75,0:27:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll come right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.75,0:27:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.70,0:27:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not pulling my leg, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.10,0:27:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.10,0:27:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.39,0:27:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.39,0:27:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank God and you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.39,0:27:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for transforming my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.39,0:27:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.39,0:27:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.39,0:27:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.71,0:27:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.60,0:27:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.67,0:28:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.67,0:28:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.67,0:28:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.44,0:28:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.44,0:28:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.56,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.56,0:28:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Chris Ranoway
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.56,0:28:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm walking between
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.56,0:28:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.00,0:28:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.00,0:28:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So is there anything beyond selfless service to others
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.42,0:28:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that can help us be prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.93,0:28:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your intention, your daily routine,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.85,0:28:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what you read, who you pray to,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.14,0:29:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it all sums up, you know, by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.63,0:29:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time the market closes, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.02,0:29:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tao has said so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.84,0:29:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spiritual Tao for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.69,0:29:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it all sums up, it all sums up,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then averages out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.79,0:29:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You got up days and down days,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.53,0:29:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and days where you feel you make a great progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.59,0:29:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and other days where you feel you went backward or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.82,0:29:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever feel like you're bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.92,0:29:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.55,0:29:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the kid in you is still active, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is bad? Kids are bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.90,0:29:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.61,0:29:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.26,0:29:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.46,0:30:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.13,0:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.78,0:30:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He just became invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.97,0:30:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.24,0:30:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.84,0:30:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.86,0:30:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.85,0:30:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just wanted to say namaste to you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.79,0:30:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and namaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.51,0:30:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.58,0:30:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.67,0:30:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.13,0:30:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.61,0:30:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to take a quick break,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.92,0:30:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll be back in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.01,0:31:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,12 and a half minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.48,0:31:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,12 and a half minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.38,0:31:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.18,0:31:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.55,0:31:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.25,0:31:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.55,0:31:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, major boats amateur are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.01,0:31:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they would have a hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.24,0:31:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They hook and pull you off the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.60,0:31:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.30,0:31:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.20,0:31:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is really simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.81,0:31:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when a student, a spiritual student,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is going through transitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.22,0:31:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.07,0:31:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to speak slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.68,0:31:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.91,0:32:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When a spiritual student going through transitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.13,0:32:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a spiritual student?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.10,0:32:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.45,0:32:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, going through transitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.23,0:32:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.51,0:32:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when you value seeing things quite different,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.09,0:32:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of make my loved ones nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.81,0:32:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.29,0:32:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.50,0:32:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Her family's a little nervous, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.03,0:32:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.65,0:32:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Going through changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.65,0:32:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.99,0:32:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.58,0:32:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.54,0:32:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wonder if there is a way of communication
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.99,0:32:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that to comfort them so they don't get so nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.54,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,about you getting become a weirdo or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.18,0:32:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a little concerned about her going
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.27,0:32:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,into a spiritual state so she's.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.81,0:32:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.83,0:32:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sit quietly in a meditative state,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing for them to panic about, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.16,0:32:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.92,0:32:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.29,0:32:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are they panicking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.83,0:33:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're standing on your head or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.70,0:33:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering because when you're ready to give
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.88,0:33:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,up a high-paying job, they get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.50,0:33:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.88,0:33:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're willing to give up a high-paying job,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.09,0:33:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.90,0:33:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.42,0:33:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you tell them you have to decide between money and God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.46,0:33:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about if they don't understand God?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.01,0:33:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they don't understand God?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.31,0:33:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.92,0:33:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.82,0:33:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, spirituality is a phenomena in all cultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.16,0:33:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, they don't live out in the middle of deserts separated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.90,0:34:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,from mankind, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.33,0:34:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.83,0:34:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So they must know that spirituality attracts a certain percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.09,0:34:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people and they should have the tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.51,0:34:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're your parents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.03,0:34:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.11,0:34:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So if they don't like what's happening, you just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.15,0:34:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,well, you brought me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.30,0:34:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.63,0:34:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.86,0:34:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.96,0:34:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If my mom asks, I'm going to say, my teacher told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.21,0:34:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.07,0:34:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they brought me right up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.94,0:34:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.34,0:34:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.40,0:34:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.42,0:34:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.42,0:34:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.78,0:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.84,0:34:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been planning quite a bit since the last time I came
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.50,0:34:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for this experience to be spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.98,0:35:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.78,0:35:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.78,0:35:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.73,0:35:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just .
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of that, people have asked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what question am I going to ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've continued to just want to be in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.46,0:35:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and be spontaneous about, you know, what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.59,0:35:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess my question is, are you the ideal spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.09,0:35:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.59,0:35:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.67,0:35:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.65,0:35:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.92,0:35:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.96,0:35:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be giving lectures on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.90,0:35:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, can I sign up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't been back there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.94,0:35:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.30,0:35:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the weather pattern back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.15,0:35:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly weather patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And can I shake your hand and have your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.63,0:36:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to shake your hand and ask for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.92,0:36:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.57,0:36:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.17,0:36:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.36,0:36:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.86,0:36:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're simple, keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.82,0:36:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.90,0:36:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy does it, and keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.28,0:36:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And live one day at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.46,0:36:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say thank you for the teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.23,0:36:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the impact they've had for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.75,0:36:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.96,0:36:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May I hold your hand and receive a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.80,0:36:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.67,0:37:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any more coffee anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.30,0:37:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.63,0:37:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.13,0:37:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thank you, and I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like to shake your hand and say thank you for your blessings,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.26,0:37:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and thank you for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.78,0:37:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the end of the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.53,0:37:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.03,0:37:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.86,0:37:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.36,0:37:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, just wanted to say thank you for your love and energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.28,0:37:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and shake your hand for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.23,0:37:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.86,0:37:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.61,0:37:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.65,0:37:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I OK like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.82,0:37:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.55,0:37:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.21,0:37:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.90,0:38:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.03,0:38:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you for giving me your blessing a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.26,0:38:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing me to quote from you in the establishment of my website,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.09,0:38:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the God Anti-Defamation League, which I was inspired to do because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of one of your DVDs a number of years ago, one of your lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.42,0:38:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,where you said, I am, you know, about all of the bad words
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bad usage of the word of God and all the things that have been attributed to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.75,0:38:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you had come down, and you are the CEO of the God Anti-Defamation League,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.32,0:38:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you aren't going to take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.13,0:38:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.90,0:38:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the God Anti-Defamation League.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.13,0:38:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I know who you are, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.86,0:38:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend the good name of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.73,0:38:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.30,0:38:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a question about marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.07,0:38:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.36,0:38:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.19,0:38:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.42,0:38:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.21,0:38:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.63,0:38:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been married.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.75,0:39:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I am at 61, and I've actually
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.57,0:39:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,been thinking about it a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never been what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never been married.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 61.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.82,0:39:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.53,0:39:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.23,0:39:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.82,0:39:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm curious to have your thoughts on what
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.32,0:39:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,might constitute a truly an ideal union, if you will,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or a workable unit at any rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.26,0:39:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And further, if you had any words that you might suggest as a vow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.75,0:39:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people want to be together with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.26,0:39:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.26,0:39:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people want to be together with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.21,0:39:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, it must be significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.00,0:39:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you enjoy being with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.86,0:39:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.71,0:39:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.25,0:39:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.69,0:39:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.61,0:39:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:40:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.44,0:40:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it is, generally.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.96,0:40:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.82,0:40:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.38,0:40:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.05,0:40:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.55,0:40:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, it's all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.05,0:40:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.55,0:40:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it is for me, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.36,0:40:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.40,0:40:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did have a couple more questions, but they limited me to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.94,0:40:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's all I'm going to do is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.71,0:40:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you this, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.23,0:40:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.94,0:40:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.44,0:40:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You once mentioned that you were really looking forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.19,0:40:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get to the other side, if you were
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.25,0:40:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be able to talk to and be around Socrates
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.42,0:40:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your old buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.53,0:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if, when I get to the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to chum with you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.15,0:40:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.92,0:40:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.42,0:40:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.21,0:40:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we have a picture, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.98,0:40:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.48,0:40:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.98,0:40:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.59,0:40:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates was short and ugly, and that always made me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.48,0:41:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, make sure he's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.44,0:41:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Short and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.01,0:41:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was short and bad-looking, ugly, Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.05,0:41:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.15,0:41:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.55,0:41:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you and I and all these people here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.55,0:41:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,could say, om, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.34,0:41:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can do the om.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.61,0:41:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.32,0:41:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you want to do the om, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.67,0:42:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.59,0:42:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.65,0:42:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.80,0:42:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.48,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say thank you for all your wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.01,0:42:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the powerful force that you are in all of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.57,0:42:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, could you calibrate chiropractic
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.36,0:42:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophy?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.05,0:42:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.15,0:42:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.42,0:42:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.96,0:42:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as chiropractic philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.92,0:42:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.55,0:42:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder of chiropractic wrote numerous books
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.44,0:42:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.94,0:42:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder of chiropractic wrote several books on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.61,0:43:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as chiropractic philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.94,0:43:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about, I can ask you a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.51,0:43:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because what we are taught in school is that there is an inborn intelligence in our body
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.92,0:43:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,which is part of universal intelligence which is God and through the power of an adjustment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.76,0:43:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're able to connect innate with universal or bring it closer together if that's is that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.32,0:43:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you're able to what connect what innate intelligence with universal intelligence yeah to universal
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.34,0:44:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence yeah that is so resist thank you may I take a picture with you all forms
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.32,0:44:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of healing are inspirational
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.71,0:44:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there's great
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.21,0:44:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,care I'd rather have a great chiropractor than a lousy MD what kind of treatments do I get I get
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.59,0:44:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of treatments what are those those are kinesiologic are they are they so I go for
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiologic treatments otherwise they'd be limping all over limping with a cane and now I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.26,0:44:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,walk pretty straight yes yes my question is about deja vus are they the experience I've had are they
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.05,0:45:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,just illusions that my ego makes or not there for real I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.69,0:45:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,get confused about she talked about the future and you can predict the future
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.51,0:45:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the question did he asked about déjà vu yeah if the deja vus you want
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.65,0:45:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to know if deja vu are really experience yes and I think if you have you know if if there's same thing with deja vu or you go and, contacting companies but I also see like you know if you wanted to talk about your
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.34,0:45:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,create your own journey through
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yesまで awesome ritual that's incredible yeah but like you know when you back in the good old days we need to maintain this сейчас
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.40,0:45:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's due to a dualistic firing of neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.76,0:45:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually when you have an experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.36,0:45:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,only one neuron pathway is carrying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.82,0:45:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and an alternate pathway is damped down,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.73,0:45:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.69,0:45:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If it fails to damp it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.34,0:45:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're getting the same information,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.28,0:46:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but via two different neuronal pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.44,0:46:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.53,0:46:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to come in episodic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.82,0:46:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so it has nothing to do with me thinking like it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.84,0:46:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamed about the future, and then it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.32,0:46:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.00,0:46:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His deja vus come in the form of his dreams about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.01,0:46:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it happens in real life,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.90,0:46:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a repeated conversation or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.65,0:46:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.25,0:46:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for like one second or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.13,0:46:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as Yogi Berra said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.40,0:46:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just deja vu
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.48,0:46:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.73,0:46:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an interesting phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.88,0:46:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which I myself have studied a little bit recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.90,0:46:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.28,0:46:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The messages are coming through two different circuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.44,0:47:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and normally one circuit is supposed to damp down,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.23,0:47:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason, which I haven't had a chance to check out,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.23,0:47:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's probably not important anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.44,0:47:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it reports dualistically from two different background time scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.44,0:47:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.30,0:47:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeming different scenes, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.94,0:47:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.03,0:47:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.36,0:47:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,May I kiss your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.09,0:47:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.11,0:47:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to touch your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.21,0:47:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.05,0:47:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.82,0:47:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, deja vu is very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.28,0:47:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it tends to come and go of its own accord
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.98,0:47:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with no particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.50,0:47:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't spent enough time checking it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.82,0:48:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has a limited value, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.84,0:48:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had deja vu, and it only happened in restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.42,0:48:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I was in a restaurant, it was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.46,0:48:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in this restaurant before,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.92,0:48:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same thing is about to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.92,0:48:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The same waitress would come up and say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.46,0:48:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.51,0:48:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a point where we stop seeking information
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.57,0:48:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of ourselves as far as spiritual truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.13,0:48:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we ask the field, and it's supposed to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.76,0:48:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.76,0:48:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm wondering is if my intention is to find the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.84,0:48:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and to come closer to God, but I'm worried that I'm really naive
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.01,0:48:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I'll be easily led astray,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.96,0:48:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I, do I just walk through that fear and go?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.88,0:48:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And led astray by what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.46,0:48:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By like the astral circus or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.65,0:49:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or like some sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.17,0:49:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The astral circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.30,0:49:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or some sort of trick, like I won't understand, and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.11,0:49:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.07,0:49:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the way to avoid the astral circus
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.32,0:49:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is avoid anything that is other than you, other.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.53,0:49:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's only yourself at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.63,0:49:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So otherness indicates a separation
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.59,0:49:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or some other spirit entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.96,0:49:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only the reality of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.40,0:49:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.34,0:49:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.63,0:49:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She had something else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.82,0:49:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.69,0:50:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.84,0:50:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.28,0:50:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, in healing and recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.38,0:50:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you talked about how to heal eyesight,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.48,0:50:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to know more about what is needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.28,0:50:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because in the book you say, I am an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.09,0:50:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not subject to poor eyesight.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.57,0:50:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this question?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.55,0:50:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.59,0:50:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.07,0:50:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there a...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.03,0:50:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I recommend for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.23,0:50:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.23,0:50:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To improve the eyesight, though you say that you're an infinite being,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.86,0:50:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not just a mere being.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.86,0:50:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.51,0:50:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So he wants to know what you did for your eyesight at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.30,0:50:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you just reaffirm that your reality is perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.28,0:50:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you only see what you need to see when you need to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.38,0:51:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not necessary to see everything all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.05,0:51:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only necessary to see what you need to see when you need to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.80,0:51:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know where the edge of the cliff is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.32,0:51:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you get close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.67,0:51:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.38,0:51:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do we go with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.92,0:51:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To fall off the cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.69,0:51:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it in Arizona?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.90,0:51:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Canyon, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.63,0:51:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know where the edge is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.30,0:51:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't try your first experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.71,0:51:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice about nine people a year go over the side of the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.51,0:51:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For many years it was reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.40,0:51:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.07,0:51:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.55,0:51:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about nine people a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.21,0:51:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.05,0:51:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about nine people a year fell off the...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.90,0:51:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.46,0:51:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Canyon for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.46,0:51:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the paper would always report it, you know, nine people fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.96,0:51:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The next year it would say eight people fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.07,0:52:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The next year it's eight, ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.51,0:52:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But at Gradsley it was around about nine people rather consistently.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.26,0:52:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've noticed that the paper, they no longer report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.78,0:52:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't reported people falling off the Grand Canyon for about over five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.84,0:52:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Over four years, over five years, okay, over five years, over six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.44,0:52:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About five years ago, they stopped reporting how many people had fallen off the side of the Grand Canyon
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.46,0:52:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because it finally had dawned on them that this was really suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.75,0:52:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These are really people that didn't slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.44,0:52:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was their way of committing suicide without being blamed for being suicidal,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.61,0:52:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,either spiritually or legally or financially or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.88,0:52:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.46,0:53:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it's very interesting that they no longer report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.90,0:53:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you recommend walking without the glasses on?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.73,0:53:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not around the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.84,0:53:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.40,0:53:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.01,0:53:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I did many things that I probably should not have written about.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.36,0:53:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason was I lost my fear of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.92,0:53:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear would keep most people within certain boundaries, but I lost fear, and I lost my fear of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.26,0:53:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fact that I was afraid, I would just do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.15,0:53:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you walk through the final door, it was more than fear, it was like terror, but you just do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.80,0:54:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear keeps most people from approaching the edge, you know, the experiential edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.17,0:54:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where the Grand Canyon only is symbolic of being close to the edge of what you're able to tolerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.26,0:54:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.19,0:54:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to, first off, express my gratitude for being in your presence today.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.67,0:54:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, if we have permission, at what level on the map of consciousness does coffee calibrate at?
