Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.34,1:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.34,1:07:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankfurt
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.19,1:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,oh Frankfurt
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.19,1:07:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I took 12 years of German in school
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.19,1:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.30,1:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.30,1:07:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reasonably fluent after a while
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.73,1:07:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I lived in Milwaukee near outside Milwaukee
