Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.11,1:08:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,receive your blessing and say thank you and to shake your hands yes
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.81,1:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,ah god bless god bless you amen that's it okay hello hey dr hawkins i just like to uh say thank
