Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.67,1:09:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,uh no i couldn't couldn't think of anything he wants to shake mine yep oh that's fine
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.05,1:09:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that's fine thank you thank you for coming up to meet me thank you mr bobblehead
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.27,1:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,i want to say
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.10,1:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you today i'm very well actually yeah i want to say oh okay i'll stop being mr bobblehead
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.65,1:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much for coming here i want to thank you as well thank you for enabling this place for
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.46,1:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.46,1:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pulled me out of many, many dark moments in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.46,1:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.46,1:10:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.46,1:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.46,1:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.46,1:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.85,1:10:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, ever since childhood, had night terrors.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.09,1:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wake up in the middle of the night in a mindless terror that doesn't have, it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.02,1:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,matter what's going on in my brain, there may or may not be thoughts there, but it's
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.82,1:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,just stark, raving terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.48,1:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a sense that there's something on the other end of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.56,1:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.09,1:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've read all of your books, almost all of your books, and the story that you tell
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.64,1:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,near the end where you say that at a certain moment comes a terror where the ego is basically
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.53,1:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to pull out all the stops to not, because it's afraid of not existing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.90,1:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.90,1:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A fear of death, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.90,1:11:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.82,1:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my question is, is there some misstep that I can take during that experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.25,1:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some what step?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.53,1:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misstep.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.53,1:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misstep.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.53,1:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.53,1:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some error.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.53,1:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Error.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.96,1:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a potential error on my part when that, when that experience is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.06,1:11:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.69,1:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.69,1:11:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and don't forget, a lot of things are just, the result of brain physiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.97,1:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing personal about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.14,1:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.14,1:11:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.14,1:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody else has nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.80,1:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it ain't me, it ain't you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.80,1:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the human condition, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.80,1:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.80,1:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's suppressed energy during the day and it discharges at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.14,1:11:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the human design, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.14,1:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.03,1:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.03,1:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.03,1:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come and shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.03,1:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.89,1:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, many of these questions could be answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.89,1:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.89,1:12:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.85,1:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to take the time and the trouble to research them, so many of the questions
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.22,1:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that people bring up, which I can't give you a ready answer, you know, within five
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.18,1:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or ten minutes, Susan, I can track it down because this question leads to this, that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.39,1:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to this, that leads to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.64,1:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you can research any question until you reach the state of satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.14,1:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.14,1:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.10,1:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a first-time visitor here, my 14-year-old daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.10,1:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, 14?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.10,1:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.10,1:12:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.10,1:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from, love?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.10,1:12:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,South Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.10,1:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.52,1:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We were watching a DVD of yours, and she takes classical Indian dancing, and you were
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.65,1:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the dance of Shiva, so she really appreciated that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.27,1:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the dance of Shiva, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.36,1:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.36,1:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year ago, I had this strong vision of Christ, a vision of Christ in this radiant
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.31,1:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow light, and needless to say, life has never been the same since then, but ...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.85,1:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a vision of Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.85,1:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.35,1:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a vision, and it was exceedingly bright light.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.35,1:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.35,1:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.35,1:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A vision of Christ in a bright, yellow light that was just extremely loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.35,1:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.35,1:13:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.35,1:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.35,1:13:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was expecting to see somebody holding a flute, so that was a perception on my end,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.35,1:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so ... I was expecting to see God holding a flute, so that was a little bit of a shock
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.35,1:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,on my end.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.35,1:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of changes going on over the last year, the last of which was, you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.35,1:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,know, a little bit of a change in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.35,1:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.35,1:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.35,1:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.35,1:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.35,1:13:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.35,1:13:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
