Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.35,1:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.35,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.35,1:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.35,1:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
