Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.38,1:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.38,1:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.38,1:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing I want to jumping in, it was during Easter, I kind of didn't, you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.22,1:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,know, know what the whole Good Friday, Easter, what it meant, and I had this overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.96,1:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,desire to just attend Catholic Mass on Easter.
