Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.73,1:14:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To attend Catholic Mass at Easter Chetesh Tube.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.73,1:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.73,1:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.73,1:14:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So ...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.73,1:14:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and I'm not Catholic.
