Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.77,1:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.77,1:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I left it in the hands of God, and I said recipe why I have this overwhelming
