Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.97,1:28:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the love you feel is that of agape.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.68,1:28:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impersonal, unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.47,1:28:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It radiates forth from the heart of man.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.23,1:28:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When we walk through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.56,1:28:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know that the trees realize that you have walked by?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.85,1:28:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the lady?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.61,1:28:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I need the lady of the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.72,1:28:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here this instant, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.59,1:28:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.26,1:28:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, she's distracted by things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.44,1:29:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.10,1:29:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show the universality of divine consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.10,1:29:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.86,1:29:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you walk through the woods, the trees know and are aware that you are walking by.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.39,1:29:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.76,1:29:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.77,1:29:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A tree is deaf, dumb, and blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.94,1:29:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it know knowing this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.81,1:29:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree knows that you are there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.03,1:29:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.34,1:29:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.53,1:29:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It came to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.22,1:29:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.69,1:29:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a very high state.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.14,1:29:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I walked through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.07,1:29:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The trees almost like genuflected.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.40,1:29:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.85,1:30:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it dawned on me that I was aware of the divinity of the life within the tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.97,1:30:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the tree was really acknowledging my awareness of the divinity of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.77,1:30:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of life is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.27,1:30:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So life as it expresses as a tree, as it's human, is still just life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.30,1:30:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a little mosquito has life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.11,1:30:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So life recognizes life and unconsciously, without saying anything, recognizes that it is a reflection of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.60,1:30:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So know that when you walk through the woods, the trees all know who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.43,1:30:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.48,1:30:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.18,1:30:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of enhances the significance of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.22,1:31:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because wherever you walk, you shine forth that light.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.51,1:31:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to live in New York City in the Upper East Side.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.56,1:31:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a certain way to go every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.69,1:31:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in a pretty high state in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.61,1:31:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I would walk down the street, the doorman down the road would start to beam.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.81,1:31:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And everywhere I went, people would beam.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.27,1:31:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd walk into the hardware store, and they would all shine forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.68,1:31:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because when you're in a high state, you pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.68,1:31:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When you shine that energy forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.15,1:31:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And people just feel a gladness when you come up to them, to the doorman.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.22,1:31:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You look to the doorman, and he just loves opening the door for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.64,1:31:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.56,1:31:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's all beyond the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.47,1:31:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the energy field that we've been talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.85,1:31:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That energy field uplifts and radiates forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.60,1:31:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So people say, what can I do to help the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.28,1:31:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, just be who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.05,1:32:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being who you are is what's uplifting the world, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.01,1:32:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you folks here, the end of the world would just fall over into the ocean, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.10,1:32:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.18,1:32:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, greetings and love from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.30,1:32:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.06,1:32:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, greetings and love from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.80,1:32:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.27,1:32:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.56,1:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.89,1:32:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.56,1:32:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a chance to go to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.85,1:32:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go there just to see the kangaroos.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.14,1:32:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.55,1:32:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a great, great pleasure to bring you to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.60,1:32:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what are we doing now?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.60,1:32:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.97,1:32:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.31,1:32:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.90,1:33:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly blessed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.14,1:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly blessed by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.86,1:33:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am profoundly blessed by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.05,1:33:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.32,1:33:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we will be forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.72,1:33:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.05,1:33:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.10,1:33:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.13,1:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.14,1:33:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.17,1:33:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.18,1:33:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.21,1:33:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.22,1:33:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.25,1:33:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.40,1:33:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.43,1:33:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.44,1:33:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.51,1:33:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.59,1:33:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.78,1:33:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.86,1:33:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.89,1:33:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.90,1:33:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.51,1:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.81,1:33:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I probably missed one.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.15,1:33:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here, I got a pen here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.10,1:33:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
